The Lady-Vok was getting annoyed. Firaxis had not reported back yet 
and Talos seemed to be preoccupied. She opened a commline.

Meteara: Cybertronian Firaxis, what is your position? (She closed the 
line) So, Cybertronian Leader, do you think we can work together, or 
do you need more arguments?

Her tone might imply the use of strength as a demonstration, but Vok 
philosophy forbade her to damage the Vector more than necessary. She 
would have to use diplomacy.
